Job Description
Source the candidates from Job Board, LinkedIn & Internal Database.Match the relevant candidate with the Job Description.Initial screening over the phone.Check the interest of the candidate over the phone/email and negotiate salaries to meet the profit target.Submit the candidate to the Account Manager as a formal submission.Arrange technical interviews of shortlisted candidates over the phone or face to face as required by the client.
Job Specification
Over 2 years of experience in recruitment preferably international recruitment.Telecom/IT recruitment experience will be preferred but not mandatory.At least Bachelors degree in HR . Willingness to work at night shifts.US market experience will be a PLUS.Good negotiation & convincing skills are required.Excellent communication skills are required.Ability to work as a team player with full coordination by taking & giving help to colleagues/subordinates.Positive attitude of achieving maximum success.Must be dedicated, confident & self motivated person.Timings : 5.30 pm to 2.30 am.
